Secure Routing: Creating protected route components and refactoring the entire application's routing system to distinguish between public and private areas.

Authenticated Backend Integration: Securely connecting to a Supabase database by adapting Row-Level Security (RLS) policies and using Clerk-generated JWTs for all data-fetching operations.

