UI/UX Integration: Embedding Clerk's pre-built UI components (like UserButton and SignIn/SignUp pages) into the existing React layout and design system.

Security Hardening: Implementing Content Security Policies (CSP) to protect the application from common web vulnerabilities.

Workflow Orchestration: Mandating the use of specific Meta-Cognitive Primitives (MCPs) for planning, file system operations, and consulting official documentation, ensuring a structured and consistent implementation process..
